Crux2
-----

This theme / window decoration is an improvement for XFce 4.2 of the old Crux one.

- pick up gtk theme colors
- use the new png composing functionality of 4.2 version
- added toggled buttons for maximize and stick

More info about xfce themes on:
http://www.xfce.org/xfwm4-theme-howto/


Changelog
---------

Version 1.0	08-jan-2005
Version 1.1	23-jan-2005
 - Renfoced contrast between active and inactive colors
 - Cleaned shadows

